🍂 KOSTROMA 🍂
☄C’est une petite ville qui fait partie de l’anneau d’or de la Russie ! Elle contient des trésors tels que des monastères et des cathédrales que vous ne pouvez pas manquer ! Pas seulement la ville de Kostroma mais tout ce  qui est autour de cette ville vous réserve pleins de surprises grâce a une architecture novateur et unique en son genre ! Si la chance vous sourit, lors de la visite de l’anneau d’or, vous pouvez visiter Kostroma ! Vous ne regretterez pas ! ☄

If real, regular, normal, boring life, (when you're at home every day, seeing the same people, doing the same things) is like sitting at home on the floor surrounded by toys... traveling feels to me like going to Toys R Us with your toy box and getting to trade stuff in and buy new things and explore whole new ideas.
-Alex Day 🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸🔸 I used to travel a lot and I loved exploring new places, doing new things and meeting new people...and let me tell ya, there are some VERY interesting characters out there! For a myriad of reasons, I don't travel so much anymore but hey, if I can't go out and see the world...I can certainly bring the world to me! ✨

With a population of roughly 65,000 or less, Positano Italy has been a popular travel destination for many celebrities and international travelers. Small towns can offer a more relaxed feel and a charm that can't be paralleled. With a mix of colors as white, pink, and yellow homes combine with the blue waters of the Mediterranean sea, this Italian get-a-way city allows visitors to walk around and explore its chic boutiques, trendy restaurants, and colorful streets.
